Package: quartify
Type: Package
Title: Convert R Scripts to Quarto Markdown Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Damien Dotta
Maintainer: Damien Dotta <damien.dotta@live.fr>
Description: Automatically converts R scripts into Quarto markdown documents (.qmd).
    Transforms code and comments into structured Quarto format with proper YAML headers and code chunks.
